headline: HP: Fiscal Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The results did not meet Wall Street expectations. The average estimate of four analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of 94 cents per share. The personal computer and printer maker posted revenue of $14.06 billion in the period.
